  <brief_title>Treatment of Posttraumatic Stress Disorder by Trained Lay Counsellors in an African Refugee Settlement</brief_title>
  <official_title>Talking About Traumatic Events - A Randomized Controlled Dissemination Study of the Treatment of PTSD in an African Refugee Settlement</official_title>
